    • Constructor Detail

      • HSAMPLE

        public HSAMPLE()
        Create an object that holds a null HSAMPLE.
        The call isNull() on the object created will returns true.
          HSAMPLE obj = new HSAMPLE();
  (obj == null) <=> false
  obj.isNull() <=> true
        To creates a new HSAMPLE, use the static "constructor" : 
          HSAMPLE obj = HSAMPLE.allocate();

    • Method Detail

      • asHSAMPLE

        public static HSAMPLE asHSAMPLE(Pointer pointer)
        Create a view of the Pointer object as a HSAMPLE object.
        This view is valid only if the memory holded by the Pointer holds a HSAMPLE object.
